{"label": "droite", "transcript": [{"text": "Merci Madame la Pr\u00e9sidente.", "start": 0.6, "duration": 1.033}, {"text": "Chers coll\u00e8gues, demain", "start": 1.633, "duration": 0.767}, {"text": "nous allons voter une directive", "start": 2.4, "duration": 1.6}, {"text": "sur l'efficacit\u00e9 \u00e9nerg\u00e9tique", "start": 4.0, "duration": 1.533}, {"text": "des b\u00e2timents.", "start": 5.533, "duration": 0.567}, {"text": "C'est tr\u00e8s simple de voter,", "start": 6.1, "duration": 1.733}, {"text": "mais ce qui compte,", "start": 7.833, "duration": 0.567}, {"text": "c'est de r\u00e9fl\u00e9chir", "start": 8.4, "duration": 0.6}, {"text": "aux cons\u00e9quences de ce texte imposant", "start": 9.0, "duration": 2.6}, {"text": "de faire des travaux majeurs", "start": 11.6, "duration": 1.733}, {"text": "de r\u00e9novation thermique", "start": 13.333, "duration": 0.933}, {"text": "sur 40 millions de b\u00e2timents en Europe", "start": 14.266, "duration": 2.534}, {"text": "d'ici 2033.", "start": 16.8, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "40\u00a0% de tout le parc", "start": 18.1, "duration": 2.2}, {"text": "immobilier en Europe,", "start": 20.3, "duration": 1.433}, {"text": "en moins de dix ans.", "start": 21.733, "duration": 1.233}, {"text": "Pour cela,", "start": 22.966, "duration": 0.334}, {"text": "la Commission promet", "start": 23.3, "duration": 1.6}, {"text": "150 milliards de budget europ\u00e9en.", "start": 24.9, "duration": 1.633}, {"text": "Mais d'apr\u00e8s ses propres calculs,", "start": 26.533, "duration": 1.4}, {"text": "le co\u00fbt sera de 275 milliards par an.", "start": 27.933, "duration": 4.2}, {"text": "Par an, chers coll\u00e8gues.", "start": 32.6, "duration": 0.7}, {"text": "Et ce co\u00fbt, que ce soit", "start": 33.3, "duration": 1.033}, {"text": "avec de l'argent public", "start": 34.333, "duration": 0.933}, {"text": "ou priv\u00e9, \u00e0 la fin,", "start": 35.266, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "nous savons bien qui le paiera :", "start": 36.166, "duration": 1.167}, {"text": "les gens ordinaires,", "start": 37.333, "duration": 1.333}, {"text": "ceux qui travaillent, qui contribuent,", "start": 38.666, "duration": 1.634}, {"text": "qui \u00e9pargnent toute une vie", "start": 40.3, "duration": 1.0}, {"text": "pour acheter le lieu o\u00f9 ils vivent,", "start": 41.3, "duration": 1.766}, {"text": "et qui vont se voir imposer les travaux", "start": 43.066, "duration": 1.367}, {"text": "dont les prix exploseront", "start": 44.433, "duration": 1.1}, {"text": "du fait de la demande brutale", "start": 45.533, "duration": 1.367}, {"text": "que ces nouvelles normes", "start": 46.9, "duration": 0.933}, {"text": "vont provoquer.", "start": 47.833, "duration": 1.133}, {"text": "Et tout cela, pourquoi ?", "start": 48.966, "duration": 1.167}, {"text": "Pourquoi ?", "start": 50.133, "duration": 1.267}, {"text": "Oui, chers coll\u00e8gues,", "start": 51.4, "duration": 0.566}, {"text": "nous voulons tous baisser", "start": 51.966, "duration": 0.834}, {"text": "les \u00e9missions de carbone.", "start": 52.8, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "Mais toutes les donn\u00e9es disponibles", "start": 53.7, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "montrent l'aberration", "start": 55.0, "duration": 1.433}, {"text": "d'une politique de r\u00e9novation", "start": 56.433, "duration": 1.767}, {"text": "indiff\u00e9renci\u00e9e des b\u00e2timents.", "start": 58.2, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Aux \u00c9tats-Unis,", "start": 60.2, "duration": 0.533}, {"text": "le retour d'exp\u00e9rience de campagne", "start": 60.733, "duration": 1.567}, {"text": "massive montre", "start": 62.3, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "que les \u00e9conomies d'\u00e9nergie", "start": 63.5, "duration": 1.133}, {"text": "sont trois fois moindres", "start": 64.633, "duration": 1.0}, {"text": "qu'esp\u00e9r\u00e9, pour des co\u00fbts", "start": 65.633, "duration": 1.267}, {"text": "deux fois plus important que pr\u00e9vu.", "start": 66.9, "duration": 2.066}, {"text": "l'Universit\u00e9 de Cambridge a montr\u00e9,", "start": 68.966, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "il y a quelques semaines,", "start": 70.766, "duration": 0.834}, {"text": "que la consommation,", "start": 71.6, "duration": 0.866}, {"text": "cinq ans apr\u00e8s les travaux,", "start": 72.466, "duration": 1.334}, {"text": "la consommation d'\u00e9nergie", "start": 73.8, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "ne baissait m\u00eame pas.", "start": 75.1, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "En Allemagne,", "start": 75.9, "duration": 0.766}, {"text": "apr\u00e8s 340 milliards\u00a0d'euros d'investissements", "start": 76.666, "duration": 2.834}, {"text": "dans la r\u00e9novation thermique,", "start": 79.5, "duration": 1.033}, {"text": "une \u00e9tude montre", "start": 80.533, "duration": 0.667}, {"text": "que l'impact n'est m\u00eame pas mesurable.", "start": 81.2, "duration": 2.133}, {"text": "La seule cons\u00e9quence incontestable", "start": 83.433, "duration": 1.667}, {"text": "pour l'environnement,", "start": 85.1, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "c'est l'explosion de l'usage", "start": 86.533, "duration": 1.267}, {"text": "des mat\u00e9riaux n\u00e9cessaires.", "start": 87.8, "duration": 1.0}, {"text": "Quel paradoxe absolu,", "start": 88.8, "duration": 1.733}, {"text": "que des politiques", "start": 90.533, "duration": 0.633}, {"text": "qui se veulent \u00e9cologistes,", "start": 91.166, "duration": 1.434}, {"text": "veuillent mettre la moiti\u00e9", "start": 92.6, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "de tous les b\u00e2timents europ\u00e9ens", "start": 93.9, "duration": 1.433}, {"text": "en chantier dans les dix ans.", "start": 95.333, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "Derri\u00e8re cela,", "start": 96.833, "duration": 0.967}, {"text": "il y a la persistance", "start": 97.8, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "d'une obsession d\u00e9pass\u00e9e :", "start": 98.7, "duration": 1.133}, {"text": "tout changer,", "start": 99.833, "duration": 1.067}, {"text": "tout refaire, disqualifier l'ancien,", "start": 100.9, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": "le patrimoine, l'h\u00e9ritage,", "start": 103.0, "duration": 1.333}, {"text": "pour tout recommencer \u00e0 neuf.", "start": 104.333, "duration": 1.967}, {"text": "C'est cette logique", "start": 106.3, "duration": 0.966}, {"text": "qui a cr\u00e9\u00e9 la crise \u00e9cologique", "start": 107.266, "duration": 1.6}, {"text": "et nous comprenons malheureusement", "start": 108.866, "duration": 2.2}, {"text": "pourquoi de grands int\u00e9r\u00eats industriels", "start": 111.066, "duration": 1.567}, {"text": "soutiennent ce projet, \u00e9videmment.", "start": 112.633, "duration": 2.133}, {"text": "Mais derri\u00e8re cette situation,", "start": 114.766, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "il y a en r\u00e9alit\u00e9", "start": 116.566, "duration": 1.467}, {"text": "une crise majeure,", "start": 118.033, "duration": 1.333}, {"text": "une crise sociale et politique aussi", "start": 119.366, "duration": 2.2}, {"text": "que ce texte pourrait entra\u00eener.", "start": 121.766, "duration": 2.034}, {"text": "La seule vraie solution", "start": 124.0, "duration": 0.966}, {"text": "pour d\u00e9carboner,", "start": 124.966, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "c'est de passer du fioul, du gaz", "start": 125.766, "duration": 1.567}, {"text": "qui chauffe nos logements, \u00e0 l'\u00e9lectricit\u00e9,", "start": 127.333, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "et d'utiliser toutes les sources d\u00e9carbon\u00e9es", "start": 129.333, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "pour en produire beaucoup plus.", "start": 131.333, "duration": 1.233}, {"text": "Mais comme par hasard,", "start": 132.566, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "ceux qui veulent", "start": 133.366, "duration": 0.834}, {"text": "r\u00e9glementer la vie des Europ\u00e9ens", "start": 134.2, "duration": 1.433}, {"text": "jusque dans leur espace priv\u00e9,", "start": 135.633, "duration": 1.4}, {"text": "sont aussi g\u00e9n\u00e9ralement", "start": 137.033, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "ceux qui combattent,", "start": 137.933, "duration": 0.6}, {"text": "par exemple, l'\u00e9nergie nucl\u00e9aire.", "start": 138.533, "duration": 1.633}, {"text": "Nous avons d\u00e9pos\u00e9 un amendement", "start": 140.166, "duration": 1.134}, {"text": "pour faire en sorte", "start": 141.3, "duration": 0.6}, {"text": "qu'un b\u00e2timent z\u00e9ro \u00e9mission soit aussi", "start": 141.9, "duration": 2.2}, {"text": "un b\u00e2timent", "start": 144.433, "duration": 0.467}, {"text": "qui profite de cette source d'\u00e9nergie", "start": 144.9, "duration": 1.566}, {"text": "parmi d'autres.", "start": 146.466, "duration": 0.834}, {"text": "Demain, chers", "start": 147.3, "duration": 0.466}, {"text": "coll\u00e8gues, en votant,", "start": 147.766, "duration": 0.934}, {"text": "r\u00e9fl\u00e9chissons aux cons\u00e9quences.", "start": 148.7, "duration": 2.3}]}